  <title>WebKit2.Settings.media_playback_allows_inline</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
Settings.media_playback_allows_inline: Boolean (Read / Write / Construct)
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Whether media playback is full-screen only or inline playback is allowed.
This is <code>true</code> by default, so media playback can be inline. Setting it to
<code>false</code> allows specifying that media playback should be always fullscreen.</p>

